Are you referring to the current behavior? To fix #41 we need to create a new request object. This is going so far as:

```python
def tm_tween(request):
    orig_request = request
    factory = registry.queryUtility(IRequestFactory, Request)
    for attempt in attempts:
        request = factory(orig_request.environ)
